$$$LIST.text:
FROM 'TSAZF.CBT.ALZ.DYNAMIC.ISPPLIB'
    ISR@PRIM - Single ISPF Primary menu Panel for Dynamic ISPF. This
               was generated by ISPDTLC using DTL in the ....ISPGLIB
               ISP@PRIM member.
    REXXEPNL - My Standard REXX Error Panel 1
    REXXEPN3 - My Standard REXX Error Panel 2

    RHELP01  - My Standard REXX Help Panel 1
    RHELP02  - My Standard REXX Help Panel 2
    RHELP03  - My Standard REXX Help Panel 3
    RHELP04  - My Standard REXX Help Panel 4

REXXEPNL.text:
)ATTR
  @ TYPE(INPUT)  INTENS(LOW)  CAPS(ON)   JUST(LEFT)
  ! TYPE(OUTPUT) INTENS(HIGH) CAPS(OFF)  COLOR(TURQ)
  ¢ TYPE(OUTPUT) INTENS(LOW)  CAPS(OFF)
  ¬ TYPE(TEXT)   INTENS(HIGH) COLOR(YELLOW)
  # TYPE(TEXT)   INTENS(HIGH) COLOR(RED) HILITE(USCORE)
  $ TYPE(TEXT)   INTENS(LOW)  CAPS(OFF)  COLOR(TURQ)
  % TYPE(TEXT)   INTENS(HIGH)
  + TYPE(TEXT)   INTENS(LOW)
)BODY EXPAND(||) WIDTH(&ZSCREENW)
%|-| REXX ERROR Reporting Panel |-|
%COMMAND ===>@ZCMD
¬| | An#ERROR¬has occurred in REXX!erexx   +| |
¬| |Please do a SCREEN PRINT, write down what you were doing, and| |
¬| |then contact Product Support http://mutualnet/is/softools.htm| |
+
$        Error Type:¢etype
$       Error Cause:¢ecause
$                RC:¢erc
$ Error Description:¢emsg

$       Source Line:¢elineno
$   Source reads as:¢sourcel

$Source EXECutes as:¢expandl

$    Stack Contents:¢eresults


+Press%END+to exit
)INIT
)PROC
)END

REXXEPN3.text:
)ATTR
  @ TYPE(INPUT)  INTENS(LOW) CAPS(ON)    JUST(LEFT)
  ! TYPE(OUTPUT) INTENS(HIGH) CAPS(OFF)  COLOR(TURQ)
  ¢ TYPE(OUTPUT) INTENS(LOW)  CAPS(OFF)
  ¬ TYPE(TEXT)   INTENS(HIGH) COLOR(YELLOW)
  # TYPE(TEXT)   INTENS(HIGH) COLOR(RED) HILITE(USCORE)
  $ TYPE(TEXT)   INTENS(LOW)  CAPS(OFF)  COLOR(TURQ)
  % TYPE(TEXT)   INTENS(HIGH)
  + TYPE(TEXT)   INTENS(LOW)
)BODY EXPAND(||)
%|-| REXX ERROR Reporting Panel |-|
%COMMAND ===>@ZCMD
¬| | An#ERROR¬has occurred in REXX!erexx   +| |
¬| |Please do a SCREEN PRINT, note exactly what you were doing,| |
¬| |and then contact MVS Technical Services| |
+
$        Error Type:¢etype
$       Error Cause:¢ecause
$                RC:¢erc
$       Source Line:¢elineno
$ Error Description:¢emsg
+
$| | Source line reads as: | |
+
¢sourcel


$| | Source line EXECutes as: | |
+
¢expandl


+Press%END+to exit
+
+
)INIT
)PROC
)END

RHELP01.text:
)ATTR
¢ TYPE(OUTPUT) INTENS(LOW)  CAPS(OFF)
# TYPE(OUTPUT) INTENS(HIGH) COLOR(TURQ)
_ TYPE(INPUT)  INTENS(HIGH) CAPS(OFF)
~ TYPE(INPUT)  INTENS(HIGH) CAPS(OFF) PAD(_)
¬ TYPE(TEXT)   INTENS(HIGH) COLOR(YELLOW)
$ TYPE(TEXT)   INTENS(HIGH) COLOR(TURQ)
)BODY EXPAND(||)
%|-|¬REXX Help List Display%|-| +
%COMMAND ===>_ZCMD | |%SCROLL ===>_Z   +
¬
+Enter$END+to exit | | &typedisp              | | Scroll$UP+or$DOWN +
+
+  Name    Type -h Short Description of REXX
+|=|+
)MODEL CLEAR(SEL) ROWS(SCAN)
~Z#rexxname¢Z+ ¢Z+¢rexxdesc
)INIT
  .HELP   = RHELP03
  .ZVARS = '(ZSCBR, SEL, type, hhelp)'
)REINIT
   REFRESH(SEL,rexxname,type)
)PROC
   IF (&ZTDSELS = 1) .RESP = 'END'
)END

RHELP02.text:
)ATTR
¢ TYPE(OUTPUT) INTENS(LOW) CAPS(OFF)
_ TYPE(INPUT)  INTENS(HIGH) CAPS(OFF)
¬ TYPE(TEXT)   INTENS(HIGH) COLOR(YELLOW)
$ TYPE(TEXT)   INTENS(HIGH) COLOR(TURQ)
)BODY EXPAND(||)
%|-|¬REXX Help Display%|-|
%COMMAND ===>_ZCMD | | %SCROLL ===>_Z   +
¬
+Enter$END+to exit$| | &rname | |+Scroll$UP+or$DOWN
+
)MODEL
¢source
)INIT
  .HELP   = RHELP04
  .ZVARS = '(ZSCBR)'
)END
